datasets.name: home_tile_views_dataset
queryLines:
SELECT
  home_tile,
  SUM(unique_tile_views) as total_unique_tile_views,
  SUM(unique_tile_clicks) as total_unique_tile_clicks,
  SUM(unique_interstitial_views) as total_unique_interstitial_views,
  SUM(unique_interstitial_primary_button_clicks) as total_unique_interstitial_primary_button_clicks,
  SUM(unique_interstitial_secondary_button_clicks) as total_unique_interstitial_secondary_button_clicks,
  SUM(unique_tile_clicks) / SUM(unique_tile_views) as home_tile_clicked_vs_homepage_displayed,
  SUM(unique_interstitial_primary_button_clicks) / SUM(unique_tile_views) as primary_button_clicked_vs_tile_displayed,
  SUM(unique_interstitial_secondary_button_clicks) / SUM(unique_tile_views) as secondary_button_clicked_vs_tile_displayed,
  SUM(unique_interstitial_primary_button_clicks) / SUM(unique_interstitial_views) as primary_button_clicked_vs_interstitial_displayed,
  SUM(unique_interstitial_secondary_button_clicks) / SUM(unique_interstitial_views) as secondary_button_clicked_vs_interstitial_displayed
FROM hpx_events_model_homepage_summary
GROUP BY home_tile
ORDER BY total_unique_tile_views DESC
